meanings: 실용회화-가벼운 화제 I think I should be on my way.
실용회화-가벼운 화제 I've got to go now.
실용회화-가벼운 화제 I should get going now.
실용회화-전화를 끊을 때 I have to go. Talk to you later.
(눈으로) see, watch, look (at), catch sight (of), (처음으로) set[lay, clap] eyes (on), (목격하다) spot, witness
